ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-chuyen-dung-giao-duc-inno-co-dac-diem-gi\/#may_chieu_giao_duc_la_gi\" >M\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-chuyen-dung-giao-duc-inno-co-dac-diem-gi\/#co_cau_san_pham\" >C\u01a1 c\u1ea5u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-chuyen-dung-giao-duc-inno-co-dac-diem-gi\/#khoang_cach_chieu\" >Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch chi\u1ebfu?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-chuyen-dung-giao-duc-inno-co-dac-diem-gi\/#mau_sac_sinh_dong_ro_rang_hon\" >M\u00e0u s\u1eafc sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-chuyen-dung-giao-duc-inno-co-dac-diem-gi\/#tuoi_tho_len_den_20000_gio\" >Tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 20.000 gi\u1edd<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-chuyen-dung-giao-duc-inno-co-dac-diem-gi\/#thau_kinh_chieu_hd\" >Th\u1ea5u k\u00ednh chi\u1ebfu HD<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-chuyen-dung-giao-duc-inno-co-dac-diem-gi\/#chuc_nang_zoom\" >Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng Zoom<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i theo v\u00ec th\u1ebf n\u1ec1n gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i trang m\u1ed9t &#8220;l\u1edbp \u00e1o m\u1edbi&#8221; v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ee7 nhu c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf nh\u1ea5t cho h\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\u00ean theo h\u1ecdc. V\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho kh\u00f4ng gian h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111a d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. Nay INNO \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ee7 nhu c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f3 g\u1ed3m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1eabn di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1o cho kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng. INNO g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu c\u00f3 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng nhu c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c cao trong \u0111\u00f3.<\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"may_chieu_giao_duc_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>M\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9238 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-4-800x248.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"248\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-4-800x248.jpg 800w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-4-768x238.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-4-600x186.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-4.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>M\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c l\u00e0 m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng cho gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u d\u00f2ng kh\u00e1c nhau cho nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u01b0: M\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c INNO LD-4200X, M\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 3LCD INNO LD-4200UST,&#8230;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co_cau_san_pham\"><\/span><strong>C\u01a1 c\u1ea5u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Liquid Crystal Display (3LCD) t\u00edch h\u1ee3p 3 ch\u00edp x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u00e0u tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t projector. Gi\u00fap \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ea7u ra c\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n th\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3 s\u00e1ng cao m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i th\u1eeba \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khoang_cach_chieu\"><\/span><strong>Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch chi\u1ebfu?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9233\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-3-467x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"685\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-3-467x400.jpg 467w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-3-768x658.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-3-600x514.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-3.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mau_sac_sinh_dong_ro_rang_hon\"><\/span><strong>M\u00e0u s\u1eafc sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9235\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-7-512x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"625\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-7-512x400.jpg 512w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-7-768x600.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-7-600x469.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-7.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tuoi_tho_len_den_20000_gio\"><\/span><strong>Tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 20.000 gi\u1edd<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd c\u1ee7a m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c Inno LD-4200X c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 10 n\u0103m<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9236\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-8-460x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"696\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-8-460x400.jpg 460w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-8-768x668.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-8-600x522.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-8.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thau_kinh_chieu_hd\"><\/span><strong>Th\u1ea5u k\u00ednh chi\u1ebfu HD<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u1ed0ng k\u00ednh chi\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ea5u k\u00ednh th\u1ee7y tinh gi\u00fap m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb r\u00f5 n\u00e9t h\u01a1n<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9237\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-9-562x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"570\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-9-562x400.jpg 562w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-9-768x547.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-9-600x427.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/May-chieu-INNO-3LCD-LD-4200X-900-9.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chuc_nang_zoom\"><\/span><strong>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng Zoom<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"center\">N\u1ebfu Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng zoom, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh chi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfu, v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<\/div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9241\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05